item.title: Fellwanderers freshers walk across the Seven Sisters
item.author: Simon Evans,
item.description: Early on Sunday morning, more than 70 sleepy freshers made their way to Victoria and began to congregate around the Fellwanderers banner which was proudly flying between two poles.
